import React from 'react'
import {MainLayout} from '../components/templates/layouts'

import {Navigation} from '../components/molecules'
import {View, Text, Image} from '../components/atoms'
import knobData from "./index.knobs.json";
const {menus} = knobData.data;

const App = () => {

  return (
    <MainLayout>
        <View className="main-header">
            <View className="main-header-content" direction="column">
                <View width="100%" height="100px" align="center" justify="space-between" padding="0 50px 0 50px">
                    <View>
                        <Navigation items={menus} family="quicksand" size="16" weight="400" variant="grey"/>
                    </View>
                    <View>
                        <Text>RIGHT</Text>
                    </View>
                </View>
                <View width="100%" flexValue="1" align="center" justify="space-between" padding="0 50px 0 50px">
                    <View>
                        <Text>RIGHT</Text>
                    </View>
                    <View >
                        <Image src="/static/illustrations/hero-image.png" className="main-header-hero" draggable="false"/>
                    </View>
                </View>
            </View>
            <View className="overlay"></View>
        </View>
    </MainLayout>
  )
}

export default App
